### Get all users
GET http://localhost:8080/users

### Get user by id
GET http://localhost:8080/users/1

### Get user's reports
GET http://localhost:8080/users/1/reports

### Create new user
POST http://localhost:8080/users/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "new-user",
  "password": "password"
}

### Update user
PATCH http://localhost:8080/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "new-user1",
  "password": "asd"
}

### Delete user
DELETE http://localhost:8080/users/16
